        <h3>What's New in 2026.03.05</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Expanded voice commands — 30+ new spoken formatting commands for hands-free text control:</li>
          <li>New line insertion — "new line" now creates an actual line break in all apps including browsers, VS Code, and Electron apps (previously sent a raw Unicode character that many apps ignored)</li>
          <li>Tab insertion — "tab" now sends a real Tab keypress for proper indentation</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
          All transcription happens 100% locally on your device.
        </p>
      ]]></description>
